# Mini RAG Chatbot


This project implements a mini Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) chatbot that answers user queries by leveraging information from PDF documents. It utilizes LangChain, Chroma, and Google Gemini API to provide comprehensive and user-friendly responses.

## Features

- Load and parse PDF documents.
- Split text into manageable chunks.
- Generate embeddings with a pre-trained model.
- Efficiently store and retrieve relevant documents.
- Generate conversational responses using generative AI.


